      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 06:20:21 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://peoplealsoask.github.io/stop-502-bad-gateway-error/</guid>
      <description>A 502 Bad Gateway error means one server received an invalid response from another. Quick fixes include refreshing the page, checking your internet, or waiting. For site owners, check server logs, restart services, and flush DNS.</description>
